"*Transform Dialog*: திறப்புகள் a dialog பெறுநர் adjust உருமாற்று, உருமாற்றம் "
"parameters (translate, rotate, scale, and transform) manually."

msgid ""
"*Snap Settings*: Allows you to change transform, rotate snap (in degrees), "
"and scale snap (in percent) settings."
msgstr ""
"*Snap Settings*: Allows you பெறுநர் change transform, rotate snap (in "
